Best Authority Training


Don't let training become your Achilles heel!


Best Authority University (BAU) is a unique combination of live internet hands-on training webinars and video tutorials that provide free training in every aspect of Best Authority.  BAU helps our customers leverage Best Authority products to full advantage, by training their trainers and by supplementing their education programs for new hires and refresher sessions.
 

Live Best Authority Webinars
Best Authority University offers regularly scheduled free live, hands-on instructor-led, web-based training classes for Best Authority.
Registration is required, click on the class below to register.
 




Best Authority 101 Version 4 (Premium Edition)



Wednesday, August 9, 2017 3:00 PM (EST)


                This is the most important class. It covers all the basics you need to create a TOA using Best Authority using the advanced feature set. Specific emphasis on the Best Authority features (Mark, Unmark and Edit TOA Entry).
            




Best Authority 102 Version 4 (Premium Edition)



Wednesday, August 2, 2017 3:00 PM (EST)


                This class covers the rest of the features in review not covered in 101. Prerequisite: Best Authority 101.
            




Best Authority 102 Version 4 (Premium Edition)



Wednesday, August 16, 2017 3:00 PM (EST)


                This class covers the rest of the features in review not covered in 101. Prerequisite: Best Authority 101.
            




Best Authority 201 Version 4 TOA Options/Schemes



Wednesday, August 23, 2017 3:00 PM (EST)


                For BA TOA Experts: Learn how to specify the format and arrangement of your TOA, and how to save your settings as a Scheme, so that you can use these settings on other documents.
            



